<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">إِسْمَاعِيلُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5657">مُحَمَّدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6527">أُمِّ عَطِيَّةَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا لَا نَعُدُّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٧٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْكُدْرَةَ وَالصُّفْرَةَ شَيْئًا».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>